&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in the business insights and data analysis tools and platforms&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with iterative hypothesis-driven product development and experimentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Taking an ownership mindset and working on whatever it takes to solve problems and delight users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience aligning a broad set of senior stakeholders via strong written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A track record of successfully launching new products or features that have driven significant business impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of emerging technologies and trends that could shape the future of the payments industry.&lt;/li&gt;
